<div id="zh-question-title" data-editable="false">

<h2 class="zm-item-title zm-editable-content">

<a href="/question/19647386">怎样才能不畏惧失败？</a>

</h2>
</div>
<div id="zh-question-detail" class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="38852" data-action="/question/detail">

<div class="zm-editable-content"> 如何才能在只有一次尝试机会的情况下做到最好，不去想失败的后果而影响发挥，使自己全情投入，全部发挥 </div>


</div>
<div class="zm-item-meta zm-item-comment-el clearfix" id="zh-question-meta-wrap">
<div class="zm-meta-panel">

