<div class="answer-head">
<div class="zm-item-answer-author-info">
<h3 class="zm-item-answer-author-wrap">


<a data-tip="p$t$pirate-henry"
class="zm-item-link-avatar"
href="/people/pirate-henry">
<img src="http://pic1.zhimg.com/042299fa4_s.jpg"
class="zm-list-avatar"
data-source="http://pic1.zhimg.com/042299fa4_s.jpg" />
</a>



<a data-tip="p$t$pirate-henry" href="/people/pirate-henry">Pirate Henry</a>，<strong title="Mind Hacker，Computational Neuroscience Researcher，爱写知乎夜用加长版答案" class="zu-question-my-bio">Mind Hacker，Computational Neuroscienc…</strong>

</h3>
<a href="javascript:;" name="collapse" class="collapse meta-item zg-right"><i class="z-icon-fold"></i>收起</a>
</div>
<div class="zm-item-vote-info " data-votecount="12">

<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$dominee-dominee" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/dominee-dominee" class="zg-link" title="dominee dominee">dominee dominee</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$miao-ye-4-19" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/miao-ye-4-19" class="zg-link" title="喵爷">喵爷</a>、</span><span class="user-block">知乎用户</span>
</span>


<a href="javascript:;" class="more"> 等人赞同</a>


</div>
</div>
<div class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="38852" data-action="/answer/content">

<div class=" zm-editable-content clearfix"> 将一切看作是实验，看作是作业而已。<br>潜意识里改变自己的观念很重要。一旦尝试并坚持这种自我暗示，你的恐惧会好很多，经历几次挫折之后，你就不会在意失败了。<br><br>另外，多丰富自己的生活，目光局限在一件事情上会让自己太过在乎。<br><br>音乐和运动会有助于调整状态。如果很是纠结，有必要咨询心理辅导。 


</div>

</div>
